  "title": "Aircraft Aesthetics Specialist",
  "description": "<p><strong>​</strong>Our client is a global leader in gateway services, who is seeking to recruit an Aircraft Aesthetics Specialist. This position is based in Singapore.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Aircraft Aesthetics Specialist</strong></p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Responsibilities</strong></p>\n<p>- Assist the Deployment Officer to ensure sufficient resources deployed to facilitate interior cleaning of the aircraft- - Monitors changes in flight schedules and update the flight handling team accordingly</p>\n<p>- Monitors the cleaning timings of the cleaning teams and ensure airline requirements of cleaning standards are met</p>\n<p>- Attend on request for any additional and/or last-minute items for the flight handling</p>\n<p>- Perform any other related duty for which he/she is qualified and detailed to do so by his/her superior.</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p><strong>Key Requirement</strong></p>\n<p>- Able to read, write and communicate in English</p>\n<p>- Comfortable in using PCs</p>\n<p>- Able to work in a team and independently in a fast paced environment</p>\n<p>- Comfortable with shift work</p>\n<p><br></p>\n<p>JJ Consulting Services</p>\n<p>EA Licence No.: 12C6207</p>\n<p>Applicants are invited to send in a MS Word resume to <strong>jobs@jjconsulting.com.sg</strong> stating position applying for/present/expected salaries and earliest available date.<br>\n <br>\nWe thank all applicants in advance and regret that only short listed candidates will be notified.</p>",
